  • @Alias(value="function-source")
 @DisplayName(value="Source - receive Function")
 @MetadataScope(keysResolver=JCoFunctionMetadataResolver.class,

extends org.mule.runtime.extension.api.runtime.source.Source<InputStream,SapJCoFunctionSourceAttributes>
